Package: pARI
Type: Package
Title: Permutation-Based ARI (All-Resolutions Inference) Method
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2021-10-25
Authors@R: c(person(given="Angela", family="Andreella", comment=c("Main author", ORCID  = "0000-0002-1141-3041"), email="angela.andreella@unipd.it", role=c("aut", "cre")))
Description: It computes the All-Resolution Inference (ARI) method in the permutation framework, i.e., simultaneous lower confidence bounds for the number of true discoveries. 
